18
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:45,199
What brings you here?

19
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,360
What’s the matter?

20
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:48,039
Is there a problem?

21
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,800
It’s nothing.

22
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,719
There was an incident over there.

23
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:55,759
Just a routine inquiry.

24
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,400
Come down.

25
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,639
Let’s talk.

26
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:10,919
This way, please.

27
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:24,120
No.

28
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,960
No, Brother Li.

29
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,479
We're all colleagues.

30
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,479
There's no need to make things so awkward.

31
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:32,960
Enough, stop trying to get close.

32
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,599
Today,

33
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,719
