38
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,719
I'm one of us.

39
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,039
We've checked.

40
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:48,120
It was one of our own who did it.

41
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:48,800
One of our own—

42
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,080
It was our own person who acted.

43
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,319
Enough with the nonsense.

44
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,000
Why are you here?

45
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,840
Explain it to me clearly, word for word.

46
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,960
Alright, hurry up and talk.

47
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:01,560
I went to buy medicine.

48
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:02,840
Medicine?

49
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,240
What kind of medicine?

50
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,360
Director Liang told me to.

51
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,520
Medicine for migraines.

52
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,639
He said

53
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,879
it was for Director Cui's wife.

54
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,960
The pharmacy closest to our headquarters

55
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,960
is right here at the East Gate.

56
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,280
So I came here.

57
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,240
Where's the medicine?

58
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,639
I gave it to Director Liang.

59
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,160
Brother Li, if you want to check,

60
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,639
go ask Director Liang yourself.

61
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,800
Did you go by yourself,

62
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,639
or did Director Liang go with you?

63
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,560
Zhao Di.

64
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,160
Come here.

65
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,040
Here.

66
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,639
You sent my man away right in front of me.

67
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,600
Looks like there are some things

68
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:48,959
you don't want me to hear.

69
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,240
No, Chief Liang,

70
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,920
