00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:45,840
Secretary Wang

198
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,759
Director

199
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:49,960
Go

200
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,080
and get the head of General Affairs

201
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,159
Bring Director Liu here

202
00:09:52,159 --> 00:09:54,440
Have him bring all the headquarters staff's

203
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:56,080
