241
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,279
Among those who left this morning,

242
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:36,720
who holds a position

243
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:39,159
that these two had to obey?

244
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:43,000
