284
00:13:41,759 --> 00:13:42,440
Chief Wang.

285
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:42,919
Please.

286
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,120
Get out of the way.

287
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,240
Director Liang.

288
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,039
Look at this...

289
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:58,000
What on earth is going on?

